            </template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <that>ARE YOU FAMILY</that>
            <pattern>YES ^</pattern>
            <template>
                Does <get name='supporter'/> live close to you?
            </template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <that>ARE YOU FAMILY</that>
            <pattern>NO</pattern>
            <template>
                <srai>YES</srai>
            </template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <that>DOES * LIVE CLOSE TO YOU</that>
            <pattern>YES ^</pattern>
            <template>
                <think><set name ='support_is_close'>yes</set></think>
                Then it is easier that you receive the appropriate support you  need. 
                Does she or he live with you?
            </template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
           <that>DOES * LIVE CLOSE TO YOU</that>
